string.value: 1.what man cannot live in a house?

string.value: 3.A mouse has a large pocket．What is it?

string.name: five
string.value: 5.What is higher without a head than with a head?

string.name: six
string.value: 6.What is dark but made by light?

string.name: seven
string.value: 7.What person tried to make you smile most of the time?

string.name: eight
string.value: 8.You have it．You read it．There're some pictures in it?

string.name: nine
string.value: 9.What animal has a head like a cat, eyes like a cat, a tail like a cat, but isn't a cat?
